{"tid":2120274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now : 梁君彥由退休變連任 係因為押後選舉需要主席在任要求開會","createTime":"2020-07-22T14:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T18:17:22.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec4843635e86ea9eac1e48bbe9905f71c6830db","tid":2120274,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"功能組別參選人同樣觸目，立法會主席梁君彥交提名。他早前接受本台專訪時指，擔任主席四年如坐過山車，個人意願是休息。我們打聽，梁君彥近日才改變主意，引起政圈猜測。<br />\n<br />\n疫情急速轉差，建制圈子要求押後投票，有人建議立法會的空窗期可引用《立法會條例》第11條處理，條例列明，立法會任期完結後至新一屆選舉日期間，主席必須應特首要求，召開立法會緊急會議，並由剛結束任期的人擔任議員，梁君彥「忽然爭取連任」，外界猜測與這個方案有關。<br />\n<br />\n【選舉埋位】梁君彥爭連任惹揣測　九西泛民建制搶末席<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398985&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398985%26refer%3DShare&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=9a0f835a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398985%26refer%3DShare&h=df23c4e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398985&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"3310f1de2787f21eca3cd41930ceba1c143132f4","tid":2120274,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSanctions pls"},{"pid":"d5370188b42d9147b2b56cbc267cf62449ef100e","tid":2120274,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"如果按照呢個機制<br />\n緊急會議期間<br />\n就算佢唔選，都一樣係由佢做主席<br />\n咁有咩關係?"},{"pid":"c0e59597814c48ace354ba8332a85a0a05b3d0fd","tid":2120274,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"別讓梁君彥跑掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"